OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FVariable cloud and showers possible
OL,7,Ffor Saturday, with the blustery winds
OL,8,Feasing. Generally dry on Saturday and
OL,9,FSunday, with patchy cloud and sunny
OL,10,Fspells. Feeling warm, especially in
OL,11,Fthe sunshine.
